trans-unit.source: Specifies whether all, some, or none of a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> control's properties can be exported.
trans-unit.target: Angir om alle, noen eller ingen av en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> kontrollens egenskaper kan eksporteres.

trans-unit.source: A value from the WebPartExportMode enumerator can be applied to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.ExportMode%2A> property to specify which properties from a Web Parts control can be exported.
trans-unit.target: En verdi fra opplistingen WebPartExportMode kan brukes på den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.ExportMode%2A>til å angi hvilke egenskaper fra en webdeler kontroll kan eksporteres.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.ExportMode%2A>

trans-unit.source: By default, the properties of a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control cannot be exported and the control's <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.ExportMode%2A> property is set to None.
trans-unit.target: Som standard egenskaper for en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontrollen kan ikke eksportere og kontrollens <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.ExportMode%2A>egenskapen er satt til None.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.ExportMode%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: To enable exporting all properties for the control, set the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.ExportMode%2A> value to All.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil aktivere eksporterer alle egenskaper for kontrollen som er angitt i <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.ExportMode%2A>verdien til alle.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.ExportMode%2A>

trans-unit.source: To export only certain properties while preventing the export of properties that contain sensitive data, you set the property value to NonSensitiveData.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil eksportere bare enkelte egenskaper mens eksport av egenskaper som inneholder sensitive data, må du angi egenskapsverdien til NonSensitiveData.

trans-unit.source: A property can be marked as sensitive through the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizableAttribute> attribute.
trans-unit.target: En egenskap kan merkes som sensitive via den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizableAttribute>attributtet.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizableAttribute>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > To enable the export feature for a Web application that includes Web Parts controls, in the Web.config file for your application, you must add an attribute to the `<webParts>` element within the `<system.web>` section, as in the following markup.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > For å aktivere eksportfunksjonen for et webprogram som inneholder webdeler kontroller i Web.config-filen for programmet, må du legge til et attributt til den `<webParts>` elementet i den `<system.web>` som i følgende markup-delen.

trans-unit.source: All of a Web Parts control's properties can be exported.
trans-unit.target: Alle egenskaper for en webdeler kontroll kan eksporteres.

trans-unit.source: None of a Web Parts control's properties can be exported.
trans-unit.target: Ingen av egenskapene for en webdeler kontroll kan eksporteres.

trans-unit.source: Only properties of a Web Parts control that have been defined as non-sensitive can be exported.
trans-unit.target: Bare egenskaper for en webdeler kontroll som er definert som ikke sensitive kan eksporteres.
